Trade/Device Name(s): FORA G90 Perform Blood Glucose Monitoring System
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): FORA G90 Perform Blood Glucose Meter
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for FORA G90 Perform Blood Glucose Monitoring System for quantitative measurement of glucose in capillary blood using electrochemical biosensor technology.
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for quantitative measurement of glucose in fresh capillary whole blood from finger and alternative sites; for use by healthcare professionals and people with diabetes at home to monitor diabetes control, not for diagnosis or use on neonates.
